data.description: Lots of upgrades in this charming 3 BR Rambler, New screen porch overlooking the beautiful privacy fenced/landscaped backyard with a large relaxing hot tub on a new deck. New metal Roof, gutters & guards. Hardwood and tile flooring. Beautifully finished full bath, Mstr BR has a 1/2 bath, all the facia, soffit and ceiling of carport have been redone. New water heater, New Shed. Freshly painted interior.
